Brother,

20
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,640
you said that homunculi 
can't use alchemy, right?

21
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:27,070
But this guy is different.

22
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:29,130
I've figured out what his secret is.

23
00:01:29,910 --> 00:01:33,190
When his right arm and left leg form a circle,

24
00:01:33,190 --> 00:01:37,160
he can transmute the outside of his body into other materials.

25
00:01:38,010 --> 00:01:42,080
He can change his body 
because he's a homunculus.

26
00:01:42,620 --> 00:01:46,160
But he can use alchemy because...

27
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:50,170
Because he has Ed's limbs 
in those places?

28
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:52,670
My...?

29
00:01:52,670 --> 00:01:55,670
Give them back! 
Those belong to Brother!

30
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,180
They are Brother's arm and leg!

31
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,180
Give them back!

32
00:02:01,340 --> 00:02:02,430
Why, you!

33
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:04,090
Al!

34
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:13,110
Fine by me!

35
00:02:13,110 --> 00:02:14,260
Brother!

36
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:17,610
Al! Please, stop already!

37
00:02:17,610 --> 00:02:22,830
What are you talking about? 
He's a homunculus. He's not human.

38
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:39,050
But still, that boy is Izumi-san's—

39
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:41,090
Maybe so...

40
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:53,900
You want my arm, do you?

41
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:55,900
It's <i>my</i> arm!

42
00:02:56,510 --> 00:03:00,220
You gained something for the price of this leg, didn't you?

43
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:06,950
You paid for your brother 
with this arm.

44
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:14,300
In that case, what are you going to pay to deprive me of my arm and leg?

45
00:03:15,950 --> 00:03:17,510
An equivalent exchange.

46
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,010
Stop jerking me around!

47
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:21,430
Ed!

48
00:03:27,850 --> 00:03:31,730
Man cannot obtain anything 
without first sacrificing something.

49
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:36,320
In order to obtain anything, 
something of equal value is required.

50
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:41,360
That is alchemy's 
Law of Equivalent Exchange.

51
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:47,460
At the time, we believed that 
to be the true way of the world.

52
